description:
Hanging by a Thread

Aired on 09/14/2005, Narrated by Jonathan Aris


On 28 April 1988, Aloha Airlines Flight 243, A Boeing 737-200,is en route from Hilo to Honolulu in Hawaii when the upper half of the front fuselage is torn off, blowing out a flight attendant. The aircraft subsequently lands safely at Kahului, Maui.
